mgui.interfaces.plots.sgt

Class SgtAxis<A extends gov.noaa.pmel.sgt.Axis>

  • java.lang.Object
    • mgui.interfaces.AbstractInterfaceObject
      • mgui.interfaces.plots.sgt.SgtAxis<A>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AttributeListener, InterfaceObject, NamedObject, TreeObject, CleanableObject

    public class SgtAxis<A extends gov.noaa.pmel.sgt.Axis>
extends AbstractInterfaceObject
implements AttributeListener
    Interface for displaying an axis on a plot. Holds an SGT axis objects and allows display attributes to be specified for it.
    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.0
